These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, dannemann, alhambra, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, may, december
1. the dannemann-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who's birthday is in march##2
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##7
4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | alhambra | montecristo       | dannemann | oliveros        |
| Birthday      | may  | march | december        | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, whist, scrabble
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, tram, ship
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person playing whist##7
2. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
3. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Game     | whist | canasta       | scrabble         | backgammon     |
| Transport   | taxi   | ship | tram | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, cain, prince
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, entrepreneur, accountant, engineer
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the engineer is somewhere between the entrepreneur and the journalist##7
3. the accountant is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the journalist is somewhere between the engineer and the baccarat-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | prince | cain | chaman  |
| Job   | accountant | journalist  | engineer   | entrepreneur |

