.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, balloon-flower, amaryllis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, bolivar, oliveros
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the fonseca-smoker and the person who growsamaryllis##7
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Flower   | bellflower | zinnia | amaryllis       | balloon-flower |
| Cigar   | fonseca      | baccarat   | bolivar | oliveros  |

