.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cycling, lacrosse, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, snowmobile, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is swimming##7
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | swimming   | skiing | cycling |
| Transport   | helicopter      | roller | airplane      | snowmobile |

