.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, colone, marseilles
House: wooden, colonial, cape-cod, gothic-revival
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the cape-cod house is the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
6. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the wooden house and the colonial house##7
7. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City      | liverpool | edinburgh      | colone | marseilles     |
| House   | wooden    | gothic-revival | colonial   | cape-cod |

