.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, basketball, parkour
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, doctor, teacher, librarian
1. the firefighter is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the doctor##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is somewhere between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is basketball##7
5. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
6. the librarian is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Sport          | parkour    | snowboarding   | golf | basketball  |
| Job   | firefighter | teacher | librarian    | doctor |

