.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
House: modern, futuristic, colonial, ranch-style
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel, thriller, martial-arts
1. the futuristic house is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
3. the ranch-style house is the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the colonial house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the modern house##7
5. the futuristic house is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| House   | ranch-style | colonial | futuristic | modern |
| Movie-Genre           | thriller   | martial-arts    | adventure       | time-travel  |

