.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, snake, chinchilla
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, tea, soy-milk
1. the owner of the rabbit is not the person drinking milk##6
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the owner of the snake is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the owner of the cat##7
6. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Pet           | chinchilla | rabbit | snake | cat |
| Beverage   | soy-milk         | tea      | milk | cola            |

