.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, billiard, go
There 4 different types of food: apple, pomegranate, garlic, pear
1. the person playing go is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person eating pear##7
2. the person playing backgammon is not the person eating garlic##6
3. the person eating pomegranate is not the person playing billiard##6
4. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
5. the person playing canasta is the person eating apple##1
6. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | canasta | go | backgammon | billiard |
| Food           | apple    | pomegranate   | pear  | garlic      |

