2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to colone and the owner of the frog##2
6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person traveling to colone##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| City   | nizza | liverpool | colone | hannover   |
| Pet   | frog    | rabbit      | snake      | lizard |

