5. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
6. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the chinese is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
