.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, tea, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, lavender, chestnut, azure
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
3. the person drinking water is not the person who likes lavender##6
4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lavender##5
5. the person who likes azure is somewhere between the person who likes chestnut and the person drinking water##7
6. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage           | water | tea  | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk |
| Color   | white  | azure | lavender | chestnut   |

