2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
3. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
4. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
5. the gothic-revival house is not the person who likes blue##6
6. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes blue##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Color   | coral | blue | purple      | aquamarine |
| House     | gothic-revival  | colonial  | farmhouse | victorian   |

