.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: poker, scrabble, go, monopoly
City: liverpool, edinburgh, nizza, prague
1. the person playing go is somewhere between the person traveling to liverpool and the person playing scrabble##7
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Game         | scrabble    | go | monopoly     | poker |
| City   | nizza | prague  | edinburgh | liverpool |

 